Production:
Masumi Fujimoto. Masakatsu Kaneko.

4
00:00:49,040 --> 00:00:51,429
Script:
Noburo Yamada.

5
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:53,556
Cinematography: Yuzuru Aisawa.

6
00:00:53,720 --> 00:00:55,392
Art: Akafuru volume.

7
